	<div class="crop"><a href="/opinion/opinion/2120975/spend-new-loan-wisely"><img src="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20210525/c1_2120975_210525070731.jpg" alt="Spend new loan wisely" title="Spend new loan wisely"   srcset="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20210525/c1_2120975_210525070731_197.jpg 500w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20210525/c1_2120975_210525070731_355.jpg 700w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/content/20210525/c1_2120975_210525070731_371.jpg 350w"  ></a></div>		<div class="list-detail">
			<h3>
				<a href="/opinion/opinion/2120975/spend-new-loan-wisely" >Spend new loan wisely</a>
							</h3>
			<p>The government&#039;s plan to borrow additional funds to cover its Covid-19 mitigation and relief programmes seems to be drawing more criticism with each passing day.			</p>
			<div class="f-icon">
				<span>25 May 2021 </span>
					<span class="ic-comment"><a href="/opinion/opinion/2120975/spend-new-loan-wisely?view_comment=1"><i class="icon-comment"></i> 15</a></span>								</div>
			<div class="box-reporter">
								<span class="img-profile">
					 <a href="/opinion/columnist/936"><img src="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/columnist/936.jpg" title="Spend new loan wisely" alt="Spend new loan wisely"  srcset="https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/columnist/936_50.jpg 350w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/columnist/936_50.jpg 500w,https://static.bangkokpost.com/media/columnist/936_50.jpg 700w"  ></a>
				</span>
								<span class="name"><a href="/opinion/columnist/936" class="link-unterline">Editorial</a></span>
			</div>
