				<h3><a href="/opinion/opinion/2120483/leaky-border-poses-risk">Leaky border poses risk</a>
								</h3>
				<p>The alarming report of new Covid-19 variants found in a construction worker camp in Bangkok and in the deep South again shed light on the problem of illegal migration.</p>
