				<!--div class="h-line"><a href=""></a></div-->
				<h3><a href="/opinion/opinion/2120547/are-the-olympics-worth-it-">Are the Olympics worth it?</a>
								</h3>
				<p>In an effort to curb the spread of the coronavirus, Japan from today is barring the entry of foreign nationals who have recently travelled to Thailand and six other countries: Cambodia, Sri Lanka, the Seychelles, Saint Lucia, East Timor and Mongolia. That brings to 159 the number of countries and regions under such restrictions by Tokyo.</p>
				<div class="f-icon">
				<span class="fa-date-showmobi">24 May 2021 </span>	<!-- show mobile -->
